# Development Workflow

## Environment
- Framework: Next.js v.15 with App Router
- UI: Tailwind CSS v4
- Component Library: Shadcn
- Language: TypeScript
- State Management: Jotai
- Package Manager: Bun
- Linter: ESLint v.8
- React: v.19

## Package Management
- Install packages: `bun add [package-name]`
- Install dev dependencies: `bun add -D [package-name]`
- Update packages: `bun update [package-name]`
- Remove packages: `bun remove [package-name]`
- Add Shadcn components: `bunx shadcn@latest add [component-name]`

## Scripts
- `bun dev`: Start development server
- `bun build`: Build for production
- `bun start`: Start production server
- `bun lint`: Run linter with auto-fix

## Code Quality
- ESLint enforces code style and best practices
- Husky runs pre-commit hooks
- Commitlint ensures commit message consistency
